Name: Dininho Space Adventure
About the game: In one of his daily observations, Dininho sees an imminent threat on a planet within his system. Taken by a mixture of euphoria and concern, Dininho jumps into his ship and without thinking twice, takes off towards what may be the most dangerous and heroic adventure of your life. Features Challenging adventure full of shots and obstacles. Collect coins and upgrade your ship. Play the way you want (mouse, keyboard and Joypad). 3 different worlds with 1 Boss each. +40 different enemies and obstacles!
